  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">South Asia Flood Relief Fund 2017</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">More than 40 million people have been affected by severe flooding in Northern India, Nepal, and Bangladesh. Recent floods near Mumbai has displaced thousands of people. This fund will provide relief to survivors in the form of emergency supplies like food, water, and medicine in addition to longer-term recovery assistance to help residents recover and rebuild. All donations to this fund will exclusively support relief and recovery efforts in the region.</narrative>
  </description>
